<lb n="0410b22" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0410b2201">唵<note place="inline">引</note>際<note place="inline">引</note>哥<note place="inline">引</note>囉葛哩摩<note place="inline">二合</note>鉢訥摩<note place="inline">二合一句</note></p>
<lb n="0410b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0410b2301">次當教授成就智法。</p>
<lb n="0410b24" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT18p0410b2401"><l>結彼觀自在大印</l><l>住等引心稱紇哩</l>
<lb n="0410b25" ed="T"/><l>紇哩紇哩紇哩字</l><l>即得觀自在成就</l>
<lb n="0410b26" ed="T"/><l>觀自在尊三摩地</l><l>結三昧印稱室哩</l>
<lb n="0410b27" ed="T"/><l>室哩室哩室哩字</l><l>稱已即得勝成就</l>
<lb n="0410b28" ed="T"/><l>觀想觀自在等至</l><l>妙等引心稱狄俱</l>
<pb n="0410c" xml:id="T18.0882.0410c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0410c01" ed="T"/><l>狄俱狄俱狄俱字</l><l>蓮華忿怒得成就</l>
<lb n="0410c02" ed="T"/><l>彼羯磨印相合故</l><l>大蓮華成而善妙</l>
<lb n="0410c03" ed="T"/><l>悉悉悉悉合稱時</l><l>即得一切悉地法</l></lg>
<lb n="0410c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0410c0401">此等大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0410c05" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0410c0501">唵<note place="inline">引</note>係<note place="inline">引</note>悉<g ref="#CB00833">𠆙</g><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
